102
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:06,375
Yeah, a lot has happened
lately, I guess.

103
00:06:06,458 --> 00:06:09,125
[TONOMACHI] Whoa! And straight
off the top of the shelf!

104
00:06:09,208 --> 00:06:10,458
It's cool, man.

105
00:06:10,541 --> 00:06:11,875
My lady's got some pretty
expensive taste, too.

106
00:06:11,958 --> 00:06:12,958
