just a residential area.

143
00:07:35,791 --> 00:07:39,333
Okay then!
I trust you've got this!

144
00:07:39,416 --> 00:07:42,583
Now. Let's get
this date started.

145
00:07:44,625 --> 00:07:46,333
[KANNAZUKI]
