147
00:07:48,708 --> 00:07:51,583
[MALE CREW MEMBER]
E-5963. Roger.

148
00:07:56,458 --> 00:07:57,916
Open the main gate!

149
00:08:02,916 --> 00:08:03,875
[TOHKA]
What's that?

150
00:08:03,958 --> 00:08:06,000
