155
00:08:12,583 --> 00:08:14,208
[SHIDO] Yeah, the red ones
are three times as fast

156
00:08:14,291 --> 00:08:15,625
as the others.

157
00:08:15,708 --> 00:08:17,583
Don't know why they'd
be here, though.

158
00:08:17,666 --> 00:08:18,958
Uh--

159
00:08:19,041 --> 00:08:20,875
