168
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:41,083
I've never seen
one of those before!

169
00:08:41,166 --> 00:08:42,791
Hey, wait, Tohka!
Come back here!

170
00:08:42,875 --> 00:08:44,791
[NAKATSUGAWA]
Nice work, Kawagoe.

171
00:08:44,875 --> 00:08:45,875
[KANNAZUKI] All right.

172
00:08:45,958 --> 00:08:47,416
