177
00:08:55,791 --> 00:08:58,416
Glad to see we're all ready
and prepared for action.

178
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:00,250
[REINE]
Speak for yourself.

179
00:09:03,708 --> 00:09:04,833
[ORIGAMI]
The signal's jammed.

180
00:09:04,916 --> 00:09:06,625
[RYOKO]
Origami, can you hear me?

181
00:09:06,708 --> 00:09:08,375
