187
00:09:18,541 --> 00:09:20,291
Oh, so does this!

188
00:09:20,375 --> 00:09:21,291
Gimmie!

189
00:09:21,375 --> 00:09:22,666
[SHIDO]
Slow down! Don't rush.

190
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:25,041
Eat as much as you
want. It's free.

191
00:09:25,125 --> 00:09:27,583
How the hell did this happen?

192
00:09:27,666 --> 00:09:29,750
[TOHKA] Shido?

193
00:09:29,833 --> 00:09:31,833
I'm having fun. Are you?

194
00:09:31,916 --> 00:09:33,125
Huh?

195
00:09:33,208 --> 00:09:34,541
This has been such a great day

196
00:09:34,625 --> 00:09:36,500
and I'm having a
wonderful time here.

197
00:09:36,583 --> 00:09:37,958
But I'm worried
I'm the only one.

198
00:09:38,041 --> 00:09:39,750
