Are you mad at me?

199
00:09:39,833 --> 00:09:42,166
No way! Of course
I'm not mad at you!

200
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:43,875
[TOHKA]
Are you sure?

201
00:09:43,958 --> 00:09:45,125
I'm positive.

202
00:09:45,208 --> 00:09:46,666
In fact I'm in a great mood!

203
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:48,583
I've just had a lot
on my mind is all.

204
00:09:48,666 --> 00:09:50,458
Promise you're
having a good time?

205
00:09:50,541 --> 00:09:51,583
Best time ever!

206
00:09:51,666 --> 00:09:53,083
