we have to try!

211
00:10:03,333 --> 00:10:05,416
Let's get the most we
can out of this date!

212
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:06,708
Yeah. Let's.

213
00:10:06,791 --> 00:10:09,041
--Great, come on!
--'Kay!

214
00:10:09,125 --> 00:10:11,458
[SHIDO] Wherever you need
me to go, I'll follow!

215
00:10:17,208 --> 00:10:19,000
Congratulations, you two!

216
00:10:19,083 --> 00:10:20,416
You won the grand prize!

217
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:23,458
