221
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:31,125
That's unheard of, you've
got to take her right now!

222
00:10:31,208 --> 00:10:32,166
[SHIDO]
Dream Park?

223
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:35,416
[CROWD] Hey! Wow!

224
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:36,500
[SHIDO] Whoa!

225
00:10:36,583 --> 00:10:38,000
[TOHKA] Look how
beautiful this place is!

226
00:10:38,083 --> 00:10:39,166
What an adventure!

227
00:10:39,250 --> 00:10:41,041
